name: National Capital Area Clojure Users Group – CapCLUG

tagline: Come for the parentheses, stay for the people.
body:
### Welcome!

We're a group of Clojure fans that like to eat, code, & chat together. Remember to join our [Meetup](http://www.meetup.com/Cap-Clug/) page!
